<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<odoo>
    <template id="service_design_engineering" name="Service - Design and Engineering">
        <t t-call="website.layout">
            <t t-set="additional_title">Design and Engineering - PETRORAQ</t>

            <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"/>
            <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

            <style>
                .pr-service-page * {
                    box-sizing: border-box;
                    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
                }
                .pr-service-page {
                    --navy: #06264B;
                    --navy-deep: #051d3a;
                    --gold: #e9a23e;
                    --text: #333;
                    --muted: #6b7a8f;
                    --bg: #f5f6f8;
                    --border: #e5e8ec;
                    background: var(--bg);
                    color: var(--text);
                }
                .pr-service-page .pr-container {
                    max-width: 1200px;
                    margin: 0 auto;
                    padding: 0 20px;
                }

                /* ===== SCROLL ANIMATIONS ===== */
                .pr-service-page .scroll-fade {
                    opacity: 0;
                    transform: translateY(40px);
                    transition: opacity 0.8s ease-out, transform 0.8s ease-out;
                }
                .pr-service-page .scroll-fade.visible {
                    opacity: 1;
                    transform: translateY(0);
                }
                .pr-service-page .scroll-left {
                    opacity: 0;
                    transform: translateX(-40px);
                    transition: opacity 0.8s ease-out, transform 0.8s ease-out;
                }
                .pr-service-page .scroll-left.visible {
                    opacity: 1;
                    transform: translateX(0);
                }
                .pr-service-page .scroll-right {
                    opacity: 0;
                    transform: translateX(40px);
                    transition: opacity 0.8s ease-out, transform 0.8s ease-out;
                }
                .pr-service-page .scroll-right.visible {
                    opacity: 1;
                    transform: translateX(0);
                }
                .pr-service-page .delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
                .pr-service-page .delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
                .pr-service-page .delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
                .pr-service-page .delay-4 { transition-delay: 0.4s; }

                @keyframes fadeInLeft {
                    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-30px); }
                    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
                }
                @keyframes floatIcon {
                    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
                    50% { transform: translateY(-6px); }
                }
                @keyframes pulseDot {
                    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
                    50% { opacity: 0.5; }
                }
                @keyframes expandLine {
                    from { width: 0; }
                    to { width: 70px; }
                }

                /* ===== HERO ===== */
                .pr-service-page .svc-hero {
                    position: relative;
                    min-height: 420px;
                    background: url('/pr_website/static/images/design_engineering_hero_hd.png') center/cover no-repeat;
                    display: flex;
                    align-items: center;
                    overflow: hidden;
                }
                .pr-service-page .svc-hero-overlay {
                    position: absolute; inset: 0;
                    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(6,38,75,0.95) 0%, rgba(6,38,75,0.75) 45%, rgba(6,38,75,0.2) 100%);
                }
                .pr-service-page .svc-hero-content {
                    position: relative; z-index: 2;
                    padding: 0 60px;
                    color: #fff;
                    max-width: 600px;
                    animation: fadeInLeft 1s ease-out;
                }
                .pr-service-page .breadcrumb-nav {
                    color: #cbd5e1;
                    font-size: 13px;
                    margin-bottom: 25px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .breadcrumb-nav a {
                    color: #cbd5e1;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    transition: color 0.3s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .breadcrumb-nav a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
                .pr-service-page .breadcrumb-nav .current { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; }
                .pr-service-page .breadcrumb-nav i { margin: 0 8px; font-size: 10px; }

                .pr-service-page .svc-hero-content h1 {
                    font-size: 56px;
                    font-weight: 800;
                    line-height: 1.1;
                    margin-bottom: 5px;
                    color: #fff;
                }
                .pr-service-page .svc-hero-content h1 .dot {
                    color: var(--gold);
                    display: inline-block;
                    animation: pulseDot 2s ease-in-out infinite;
                }
                .pr-service-page .gold-line {
                    width: 70px;
                    height: 3px;
                    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), transparent);
                    margin: 25px 0 25px;
                    animation: expandLine 1s ease-out 0.5s both;
                }
                .pr-service-page .svc-hero-content p {
                    font-size: 15px;
                    line-height: 1.7;
                    color: #e0e6ef;
                    max-width: 450px;
                }

                /* ===== 4 FEATURE CARDS ===== */
                .pr-service-page .features-section {
                    background: #fff;
                    padding: 50px 0;
                    margin-top: -60px;
                    position: relative;
                    z-index: 3;
                    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
                    border-radius: 12px;
                    max-width: 1200px;
                    margin-left: auto;
                    margin-right: auto;
                }
                .pr-service-page .features-grid {
                    display: grid;
                    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
                    gap: 30px;
                    padding: 0 40px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .feature-card {
                    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
                    padding: 15px;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    position: relative;
                }
                .pr-service-page .feature-card:hover {
                    transform: translateY(-8px);
                }
                .pr-service-page .feature-card .feat-icon {
                    width: 55px; height: 55px;
                    background: #fff;
                    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
                    margin-bottom: 20px;
                    transition: all 0.4s ease;
                    position: relative;
                    overflow: hidden;
                }
                .pr-service-page .feature-card .feat-icon::before {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    inset: 0;
                    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #d8902f);
                    transform: scale(0);
                    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
                    border-radius: 50%;
                }
                .pr-service-page .feature-card:hover .feat-icon {
                    transform: rotate(10deg) scale(1.1);
                    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(233,162,62,0.4);
                }
                .pr-service-page .feature-card:hover .feat-icon::before {
                    transform: scale(2);
                }
                .pr-service-page .feature-card .feat-icon i {
                    color: var(--gold);
                    font-size: 22px;
                    transition: color 0.4s ease;
                    position: relative;
                    z-index: 2;
                }
                .pr-service-page .feature-card:hover .feat-icon i {
                    color: #fff;
                }
                .pr-service-page .feature-card p {
                    color: var(--muted);
                    font-size: 15px;
                    line-height: 1.7;
                }

                /* ===== ENGINEERING SERVICES SECTION ===== */
                .pr-service-page .eng-services-section {
                    background: #fff;
                    padding: 45px;
                    margin: 30px auto;
                    max-width: 1200px;
                    border-radius: 12px;
                    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
                }
                .pr-service-page .eng-services-section h2 {
                    color: var(--navy);
                    font-size: 28px;
                    font-weight: 800;
                    margin-bottom: 8px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .eng-services-section .title-line {
                    width: 50px; height: 3px;
                    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), transparent);
                    margin-bottom: 35px;
                    border-radius: 2px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .services-columns {
                    display: grid;
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 280px;
                    gap: 40px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .services-columns ul {
                    list-style: none;
                    padding: 0; margin: 0;
                }
                .pr-service-page .services-columns li {
                    display: flex;
                    align-items: flex-start;
                    gap: 10px;
                    color: var(--text);
                    font-size: 13.5px;
                    padding: 8px 0;
                    line-height: 1.5;
                    transition: all 0.3s ease;
                    border-radius: 4px;
                    padding-left: 4px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .services-columns li:hover {
                    color: var(--navy);
                    transform: translateX(5px);
                }
                .pr-service-page .services-columns li i {
                    color: var(--gold);
                    font-size: 14px;
                    margin-top: 3px;
                    flex-shrink: 0;
                    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .services-columns li:hover i {
                    transform: scale(1.3);
                }

                /* Right dark card */
                .pr-service-page .end-to-end-card {
                    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0a3d6e 100%);
                    border-radius: 12px;
                    padding: 35px 25px;
                    text-align: center;
                    display: flex;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    justify-content: center;
                    align-items: center;
                    position: relative;
                    overflow: hidden;
                    transition: all 0.4s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .end-to-end-card::before {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    top: -50%;
                    right: -50%;
                    width: 200%;
                    height: 200%;
                    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(233,162,62,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
                    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .end-to-end-card:hover {
                    transform: translateY(-5px);
                    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(6,38,75,0.3);
                }
                .pr-service-page .end-to-end-card:hover::before {
                    transform: rotate(180deg);
                }
                .pr-service-page .end-to-end-card .ete-icon {
                    width: 75px; height: 75px;
                    background: rgba(233,162,62,0.15);
                    border-radius: 50%;
                    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
                    margin-bottom: 20px;
                    transition: all 0.4s ease;
                    position: relative;
                    z-index: 2;
                    border: 2px solid rgba(233,162,62,0.3);
                }
                .pr-service-page .end-to-end-card:hover .ete-icon {
                    background: var(--gold);
                    transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1.1);
                    border-color: var(--gold);
                }
                .pr-service-page .end-to-end-card .ete-icon i {
                    color: var(--gold);
                    font-size: 30px;
                    transition: color 0.4s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .end-to-end-card:hover .ete-icon i {
                    color: #fff;
                }
                .pr-service-page .end-to-end-card p {
                    color: #fff;
                    font-size: 15px;
                    line-height: 1.7;
                    position: relative;
                    z-index: 2;
                }

                /* ===== TWO BOTTOM SECTIONS ===== */
                .pr-service-page .bottom-grid {
                    display: grid;
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                    gap: 25px;
                    max-width: 1200px;
                    margin: 0 auto 40px;
                    padding: 0 20px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card {
                    background: #fff;
                    border-radius: 12px;
                    padding: 35px;
                    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
                    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
                    position: relative;
                    overflow: hidden;
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card::before {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    top: 0;
                    left: 0;
                    right: 0;
                    height: 3px;
                    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), transparent);
                    transform: scaleX(0);
                    transform-origin: left;
                    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card:hover::before {
                    transform: scaleX(1);
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card:hover {
                    transform: translateY(-5px);
                    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card-header {
                    display: flex;
                    align-items: center;
                    gap: 15px;
                    margin-bottom: 20px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card-header .dc-icon {
                    width: 48px; height: 48px;
                    background: rgba(233,162,62,0.12);
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
                    transition: all 0.4s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card:hover .dc-icon {
                    background: var(--gold);
                    transform: rotate(10deg) scale(1.1);
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card-header .dc-icon i {
                    color: var(--gold);
                    font-size: 22px;
                    transition: color 0.4s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card:hover .dc-icon i {
                    color: #fff;
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card-header h3 {
                    color: var(--navy);
                    font-size: 20px;
                    font-weight: 800;
                }
                .pr-service-page .detail-card p.desc {
                    color: var(--muted);
                    font-size: 13.5px;
                    line-height: 1.7;
                    margin-bottom: 20px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .assist-title {
                    color: var(--gold);
                    font-size: 13px;
                    font-weight: 600;
                    margin-bottom: 15px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .two-col-list {
                    display: grid;
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                    gap: 5px 20px;
                    margin-bottom: 20px;
                    padding: 0;
                }
                .pr-service-page .two-col-list li,
                .pr-service-page .single-list li {
                    list-style: none;
                    display: flex;
                    align-items: flex-start;
                    gap: 8px;
                    color: var(--text);
                    font-size: 12.5px;
                    padding: 6px 0;
                    line-height: 1.5;
                    transition: all 0.3s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .two-col-list li:hover,
                .pr-service-page .single-list li:hover {
                    color: var(--navy);
                    transform: translateX(4px);
                }
                .pr-service-page .two-col-list li i,
                .pr-service-page .single-list li i {
                    color: var(--gold);
                    font-size: 12px;
                    margin-top: 3px;
                    flex-shrink: 0;
                    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .two-col-list li:hover i,
                .pr-service-page .single-list li:hover i {
                    transform: scale(1.3);
                }
                .pr-service-page .card-image {
                    width: 100%;
                    height: 160px;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    overflow: hidden;
                    margin: 15px 0;
                    position: relative;
                }
                .pr-service-page .card-image::after {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    inset: 0;
                    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(6,38,75,0.2), transparent);
                    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .card-image:hover::after {
                    opacity: 0;
                }
                .pr-service-page .card-image img {
                    width: 100%; height: 100%;
                    object-fit: cover;
                    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .card-image:hover img {
                    transform: scale(1.1);
                }

                /* Execution Planning mini cards */
                .pr-service-page .exec-item {
                    display: flex;
                    gap: 15px;
                    padding: 18px 0;
                    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
                    transition: all 0.3s ease;
                    border-radius: 6px;
                    padding-left: 8px;
                    margin-left: -8px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .exec-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
                .pr-service-page .exec-item:hover {
                    background: rgba(233,162,62,0.04);
                    transform: translateX(5px);
                }
                .pr-service-page .exec-item .ex-icon {
                    width: 45px; height: 45px;
                    background: rgba(233,162,62,0.12);
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
                    flex-shrink: 0;
                    transition: all 0.4s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .exec-item:hover .ex-icon {
                    background: var(--gold);
                    transform: rotate(-10deg) scale(1.1);
                }
                .pr-service-page .exec-item .ex-icon i {
                    color: var(--gold);
                    font-size: 18px;
                    transition: color 0.4s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .exec-item:hover .ex-icon i {
                    color: #fff;
                }
                .pr-service-page .exec-item p {
                    color: var(--text);
                    font-size: 15px;
                    line-height: 1.7;
                    margin: 0;
                }

                /* ===== CTA BANNER ===== */
                .pr-service-page .cta-banner {
                    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0a3d6e 100%);
                    padding: 35px 60px;
                    display: flex;
                    align-items: center;
                    justify-content: space-between;
                    flex-wrap: wrap;
                    gap: 20px;
                    position: relative;
                    overflow: hidden;
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-banner::before {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    top: -50%;
                    right: -10%;
                    width: 400px;
                    height: 400px;
                    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(233,162,62,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
                    animation: floatIcon 6s ease-in-out infinite;
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-left {
                    display: flex;
                    align-items: center;
                    gap: 22px;
                    position: relative;
                    z-index: 2;
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-icon {
                    width: 60px; height: 60px;
                    background: rgba(233,162,62,0.15);
                    border-radius: 12px;
                    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
                    transition: all 0.4s ease;
                    border: 1px solid rgba(233,162,62,0.3);
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-banner:hover .cta-icon {
                    background: var(--gold);
                    transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1.1);
                    border-color: var(--gold);
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-icon i {
                    color: var(--gold);
                    font-size: 24px;
                    transition: color 0.4s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-banner:hover .cta-icon i {
                    color: #fff;
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-text h3 {
                    color: #fff;
                    font-size: 22px;
                    font-weight: 700;
                    margin-bottom: 5px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-text p {
                    color: #cbd5e1;
                    font-size: 15px;
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-btn {
                    background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--gold), #d8902f);
                    color: #fff;
                    padding: 14px 30px;
                    border-radius: 50px;
                    font-size: 14px;
                    font-weight: 600;
                    display: inline-flex;
                    align-items: center;
                    gap: 10px;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
                    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(233,162,62,0.4);
                    position: relative;
                    overflow: hidden;
                    z-index: 2;
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-btn::before {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    top: 0;
                    left: -100%;
                    width: 100%;
                    height: 100%;
                    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
                    transition: left 0.5s;
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-btn:hover::before { left: 100%; }
                .pr-service-page .cta-btn:hover {
                    color: #fff;
                    transform: translateY(-3px);
                    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(233,162,62,0.6);
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-btn i {
                    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
                }
                .pr-service-page .cta-btn:hover i {
                    transform: translateX(5px);
                }

                /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
                @media (max-width: 992px) {
                    .pr-service-page .svc-hero-content { padding: 0 30px; }
                    .pr-service-page .svc-hero-content h1 { font-size: 40px; }
                    .pr-service-page .features-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); padding: 0 25px; }
                    .pr-service-page .services-columns { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
                    .pr-service-page .bottom-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
                    .pr-service-page .cta-banner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; padding: 30px; }
                }
                @media (max-width: 600px) {
                    .pr-service-page .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
                    .pr-service-page .services-columns { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
                    .pr-service-page .two-col-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
                    .pr-service-page .svc-hero-content h1 { font-size: 32px; }
                    .pr-service-page .eng-services-section { padding: 25px; }
                    .pr-service-page .detail-card { padding: 25px; }
                }
            </style>

            <div class="pr-service-page">

                <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
                <section class="svc-hero">
                    <div class="svc-hero-overlay"></div>
                    <div class="svc-hero-content">
                        <div class="breadcrumb-nav">
                            <a href="/">Home</a>
                            <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
                            <a href="/services">Services</a>
                            <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
                            <span class="current">Design and Engineering</span>
                        </div>
                        <h1>Design and<br/>Engineering<span class="dot">.</span></h1>
                        <div class="gold-line"></div>
                        <p>Multi-disciplinary engineering, design and consultancy services delivering innovative, safe and cost-effective solutions across the industrial and infrastructure sectors.</p>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- ===== 4 FEATURE CARDS ===== -->
                <section class="features-section">
                    <div class="features-grid">
                        <div class="feature-card scroll-fade delay-1">
                            <div class="feat-icon"><i class="fa fa-pencil-ruler"></i></div>
                            <p>PETRORAQ Engineering Co. Ltd. provides a comprehensive multi-disciplinary engineering, design and consultancy services. When required, PETRORAQ utilizes support from group companies and international affiliates to accomplish projects of any magnitude.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card scroll-fade delay-2">
                            <div class="feat-icon"><i class="fa fa-shield-alt"></i></div>
                            <p>During detailed engineering, strict adherence to Client and applicable industry standards, codes and procedures is maintained. Compliance with engineering works, detailed by project 'Scope of Work', together with reviews to determine constructability, Value Engineering, Plant Operability and Safety (HAZOP) are deemed paramount in the execution of the project.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card scroll-fade delay-3">
                            <div class="feat-icon"><i class="fa fa-clipboard-check"></i></div>
                            <p>PETRORAQ recognizes that quality assurance is an integral part of the design engineering process and that a commitment to quality is required from all employees. Quality assurance procedures and manuals have been developed to conform to those requirements defined.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card scroll-fade delay-4">
                            <div class="feat-icon"><i class="fa fa-desktop"></i></div>
                            <p>PETRORAQ Computer Aided Design (CAD) facilities in conjunction with computer and communication networks, standard design methods and project quality design plan provide a uniform and coordinated engineering work process environment for a smooth execution of a project.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- ===== ENGINEERING SERVICES LIST ===== -->
                <section class="eng-services-section scroll-fade">
                    <h2>Our Engineering &amp; Design Services</h2>
                    <div class="title-line"></div>

                    <div class="services-columns">
                        <!-- Column 1 -->
                        <ul>
                            <li><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i>Feasibility Studies and Project Proposals</li>
